[
    {
        "text": "ï»¿Growing up in a family with three generations,...",
        "startTime": 8061,
        "endTime": 9789,
        "slowStartTime": 12241,
        "slowEndTime": 14908
    },
    {
        "text": "...I've always been very close to my grandfather.",
        "startTime": 10033,
        "endTime": 11934,
        "slowStartTime": 15200,
        "slowEndTime": 18126
    },
    {
        "text": "When I was four years old, my grandfather and I were walking in a park in Japan...",
        "startTime": 12395,
        "endTime": 15613,
        "slowStartTime": 18742,
        "slowEndTime": 23644
    },
    {
        "text": "...when he suddenly got lost.",
        "startTime": 15902,
        "endTime": 17064,
        "slowStartTime": 24003,
        "slowEndTime": 25821
    },
    {
        "text": "It was one of the scariest moments I've ever experienced in my life,...",
        "startTime": 17637,
        "endTime": 20109,
        "slowStartTime": 26605,
        "slowEndTime": 30389
    },
    {
        "text": "...and it was also the first instance that informed us...",
        "startTime": 20421,
        "endTime": 22596,
        "slowStartTime": 30782,
        "slowEndTime": 34119
    },
    {
        "text": "...that my grandfather had Alzheimer's disease.",
        "startTime": 22691,
        "endTime": 24689,
        "slowStartTime": 34186,
        "slowEndTime": 37259
    },
    {
        "text": "Over the past 12 years, his condition got worse and worse,...",
        "startTime": 25574,
        "endTime": 28787,
        "slowStartTime": 38511,
        "slowEndTime": 43405
    },
    {
        "text": "...and his wandering in particular caused my family a lot of stress.",
        "startTime": 29020,
        "endTime": 32167,
        "slowStartTime": 43680,
        "slowEndTime": 48475
    },
    {
        "text": "Then one night, about two years ago,...",
        "startTime": 33423,
        "endTime": 35376,
        "slowStartTime": 50285,
        "slowEndTime": 53289
    },
    {
        "text": "...I was looking after my grandfather and I saw him stepping out of the bed.",
        "startTime": 36374,
        "endTime": 39348,
        "slowStartTime": 54711,
        "slowEndTime": 59247
    },
    {
        "text": "The moment his foot landed on the floor,...",
        "startTime": 39805,
        "endTime": 41333,
        "slowStartTime": 59857,
        "slowEndTime": 62225
    },
    {
        "text": "...I thought, \"Why don't I put a pressure sensor on the heel of his foot?\"",
        "startTime": 41445,
        "endTime": 44372,
        "slowStartTime": 62318,
        "slowEndTime": 66783
    },
    {
        "text": "Once he stepped onto the floor and out of the bed,...",
        "startTime": 45039,
        "endTime": 46869,
        "slowStartTime": 67708,
        "slowEndTime": 70529
    },
    {
        "text": "...the pressure sensor would detect an increase in pressure caused by body weight,...",
        "startTime": 47186,
        "endTime": 50201,
        "slowStartTime": 70929,
        "slowEndTime": 75526
    },
    {
        "text": "...and then wirelessly send an audible alert to the caregiver's smartphone.",
        "startTime": 50519,
        "endTime": 53756,
        "slowStartTime": 75929,
        "slowEndTime": 80859
    },
    {
        "text": "That way, my aunt could sleep much better at night...",
        "startTime": 54261,
        "endTime": 56241,
        "slowStartTime": 81542,
        "slowEndTime": 84587
    },
    {
        "text": "...without having to worry about my grandfather's wandering.",
        "startTime": 56475,
        "endTime": 58671,
        "slowStartTime": 84862,
        "slowEndTime": 88231
    },
    {
        "text": "So now I'd like to perform a demonstration of the sock.",
        "startTime": 59234,
        "endTime": 61220,
        "slowStartTime": 89001,
        "slowEndTime": 92055
    },
    {
        "text": "So, once the patient steps onto the floor,...",
        "startTime": 63186,
        "endTime": 65569,
        "slowStartTime": 94929,
        "slowEndTime": 98579
    },
    {
        "text": "...an alert is sent to the caregiver's smartphone.",
        "startTime": 68533,
        "endTime": 70307,
        "slowStartTime": 102950,
        "slowEndTime": 105685
    },
    {
        "text": "One thing I'll never forget...",
        "startTime": 72537,
        "endTime": 73659,
        "slowStartTime": 108956,
        "slowEndTime": 110714
    },
    {
        "text": "...is when my device first caught my grandfather's wandering out of bed at night.",
        "startTime": 73933,
        "endTime": 76799,
        "slowStartTime": 111049,
        "slowEndTime": 115423
    },
    {
        "text": "At that moment, I was really struck by the power of technology...",
        "startTime": 77419,
        "endTime": 80372,
        "slowStartTime": 116279,
        "slowEndTime": 120783
    },
    {
        "text": "...to change lives for the better.",
        "startTime": 80612,
        "endTime": 81730,
        "slowStartTime": 121068,
        "slowEndTime": 122820
    },
    {
        "text": "People living happily and healthily: that's the world that I imagine.",
        "startTime": 82507,
        "endTime": 85941,
        "slowStartTime": 123911,
        "slowEndTime": 129136
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you very much.",
        "startTime": 86537,
        "endTime": 87131,
        "slowStartTime": 129955,
        "slowEndTime": 130922
    }
]